item.title: JH Biostat Computing Club 2018-19
item.description: I and Guoqing Wang we are hosting the Department of Biostatistics students Computing Club for 2018-19 academic year. Computing Club is one-hour session which gives students opportunities to share and develop computing skills useful for biostatisticians. It is held every other Tuesday 12:15-1:15 PM at JH SPH. Importantly, food üçïüçå is provided in every session! Please let us know (mkaras2@jhu.edu, gwang37@jhmi.edu) if you are interested in presenting! As always, suggestions for topics are welcome - please share us your ideas!
